Better check for incomplete Unicode byte sequences

Problem: Buffer read may split multibyte characters and the incomplete Unicode codepoint
raises ArgumentError: invalid byte sequence in UTF-8

Cause: Match on INCOMPLETE_UTF8 could miss invalid codepoints

Solution: Replace with String#valid_encoding?
